tool_input.old_string:
## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "meraki_appliance_single_lan" "example" {
  network_id             = "L_123456"
  appliance_ip           = "192.168.128.1"
  subnet                 = "192.168.128.0/24"
  ipv6_enabled           = true
  mandatory_dhcp_enabled = false
}
```
tool_input.new_string:
## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "meraki_appliance_single_lan" "example" {
  network_id             = "L_123456"
  appliance_ip           = "192.168.128.1"
  subnet                 = "192.168.128.0/24"
  ipv6_enabled           = true
  mandatory_dhcp_enabled = false
  
  ipv6_prefix_assignments = [
    {
      disabled              = false
      autonomous            = true
      origin_type           = "internet"
      origin_interfaces     = ["wan1"]
    }
  ]
}
```
